snippet.title: Stoked: Big Air Edition - X360 / PC - Never land Trailer
snippet.description:
Download the PC version here: http://www.stoked-game.com

You want to ride, but you can't take vacation? Don't worry Stoked: Big Air Edition is on the way to give you fresh and unique experience! Just keep a window open to add the feeling of winter cold air on you face.
Show some skills and you will get your very own helicopter to drop wherever you want !

Stoked: Big Air Edition is available now on X360 and PC. Visit the official website http://www.stoked-game.com for more information.
